title: GoPro Music: Amazing Alphorn Beatbox
description:
Take in the beautiful scenery of Le Creux-du-Van, Switzerland as Arthur Henry blends beatboxing with his didgeridoo playing styles on the Swiss alphorn.

Special thanks to Julien Ledermann.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera
